name: Rare Wimmzies
description: It's what's inside that counts, and the interior mists of the Rare Wimmzies are every bit as bubbly and vivacious as those of their Common cousins. Understandably, there's nothing saying that you can't decorate what's on the outside! Each Rare Wimmzy adorns itself to studying advanced balloon modeling techniques like twisting and gymping to customize its vibrant exteriors.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 12 hr 30 min, Enhanced Time: 9 hr 22 min 30 sec
